import { Grid, IconButton, InputAdornment, TextField } from '@mui/material'
import InserEmoticionIcon from '@mui/icons-material/insertEmoticionIcon'
import ImageIcon from '@mui/icons-material/ImageIcon'
import SendIcon from '@mui/icons-material/SendIcon'
import React from 'react'

export default function ChatInput() {
  return (
    <Grid container sx={{ p: '20px' }}>
      <Grid item xs={12} sx={{ position: 'relative' }}>
        <TextField
          InputProps={{
            startAdornment: (
              <InputAdornment position="start">
                <IconButton>
                  <InserEmoticionIcon />
                </IconButton>
                <IconButton>
                  <ImageIcon />
                </IconButton>
              </InputAdornment>
            ),
            endAdorment: (
              <InputAdornment position="start">
                <IconButton>
                  <SendIcon />
                </IconButton>
              </InputAdornment>
            ),
          }}
          label="메세지 입력"
          fullWidth
        />
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
  )
}
